<span id="freeTextContainer9850867338138630859">This was a nostalgic trip in time to 1980s crime and policing. I really liked the writing style, which suited the fast paced, hard nosed characters and plot. There was enough technical detail to make the book very plausible. Highly recommend for crime readers.</span>

