<div id="review_3586025384" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3586025384" />
    <a title="Buttercup" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/116359346-buttercup"><img alt="Buttercup" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1595940294p2/116359346.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3586025384?book_show_action=true">Oct 08, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Buttercup" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Buttercup" href="/user/show/116359346-buttercup">Buttercup</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3586025384" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16357652290886996652">Median Gray has a very authentic plot. The story is clever and suspenseful. The location grimy and dark with danger lurking around every corner. The characters are well developed and fit perfectly in their setting with complex and strained mentalities. I really enjoyed the tension and action that the book has is spades. Confidently recommend. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


