        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3549949367" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8664182433629989114">Median Gray is interesting. Mesce&apos;s writing style reminded me of something but I can&apos;t quite put my finger on it. The story was interesting, and the characters engaging. You get a bit wrapped up in the odd narration style and before you know it you&apos;re chapters deep and it&apos;s hours later. If you enjoy police procedurals, then this will be right up your alley. If you&apos;re more into straight thrillers this may not be your cup of tea.</span>
  <span id="freeText8664182433629989114" style="display:none">Median Gray is interesting. Mesce's writing style reminded me of something but I can't quite put my finger on it. The story was interesting, and the characters engaging. You get a bit wrapped up in the odd narration style and before you know it you're chapters deep and it's hours later. If you enjoy police procedurals, then this will be right up your alley. If you're more into straight thrillers this may not be your cup of tea.</span>
