<span id="freeTextContainer13982032013812070340">Median Gray was quite the ride... mixing police, corruption, the mob, and revenge! It&apos;s well written and fast-paced with believable characters created to feel like they&apos;re real people with entertaining dialogue, characteristics, and actions. This book reads quickly and will have you entertained the whole time! I definitely recommend this book!<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText13982032013812070340" style="display:none">Median Gray was quite the ride... mixing police, corruption, the mob, and revenge! It's well written and fast-paced with believable characters created to feel like they're real people with entertaining dialogue, characteristics, and actions. This book reads quickly and will have you entertained the whole time! I definitely recommend this book!<br /></span>
